    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Raja maderensis (MMF 42926). Juvenile male (371 mm DL), caught off the south coast of Madeira. Funchal fish market, 18.12.2013. Scale bar 50 mm." ;
